skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: pine time
des:
Is your inbox full of too many club meeting emails? Are you missing out on cool events because you simply can't check every Blitz? Not to worry, because PineTime is here to aggregate all the student events happening on Dartmouth campus.

** Learn what's happening today **
Just say, "Alexa, ask PineTime to tell me what events are happening today" to hear a list of all the fun goings-on on campus, from club meetings to Gile sunrikes to athletics events.

** Hear a random event **
We're all for broadening horizons here. If you feel like going outside of your comfort zone and trying a new club or cheering on a new sport, you can ask Alexa for a random event happening on campus. You just might find a favorite new activity!

** Subscribe to the Calendar **
Ask Alexa to subscribe to the PineTime calendar and you'll get a link sent to your phone to keep up to date with all the latest happenings on campus.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
